==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Kitty
<hw>Kit"ty</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>A kitten;
also, a pet name or calling name for the cat.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <ety>[Etym. uncertain.]</ety> <fld>(Gaming)</fld>
<def>The percentage taken out of a pool to pay for refreshments, or for
the expenses of the table;</def> <specif>by extension,</specif> <def>any
pool of money aggregated from small contributions.</def> <rj><au>R. F.
Foster.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>Webster 1913 Suppl.</source> <source>+PJC</source>]</p>

